How To Buy

About

Token main features:

Developed on the Binance Smart Chain, RabbitKing is a BEP-20 community token with a 6% transaction tax (buy and sell).

The circulation of RabbitKing is 100 trillion. 55.7% of RabbitKing is now burned. The community of RabbitKing has elected to transfer contract ownership to a dead address. For a year, liquidity is locked.
Token distribution based on Pos+Defi-based processes will be made entirely decentralised by RabbitKing innovation. Rabbitking does not offer private placement or public offering, participants are requirement to buy on the open market to ensure fair and complete distribution.

PROOF OF STAKE

The network allows participation from community users, ensuring a goes both ways and decentralised blockchain.

DECENTRALISED GOVERNANCE​

Members of the community (token holders) can submit proposals, assign authority, cast votes on blockchain- related issues and events, and participate in governance processes.

CROSS-CHAIN COMPATIBILTY

By wrapping via the RabbitKing bridge and sending back to the RabbitKing network as needed, RabbitKing can be used with ease on the RabbitKing network.

EVM COMPATIBLE

Existing smart contracts for Ethereum can be readily transferred to RabbitKing without requiring any additional modifications.

Buy Now and Take part ✌️

How to buy Rabbit King Token

Rabbitking Token is currently only listed on DEXs. We may soon be listed on the CEXs!

⇒ Create a Binance Smart Chain (BSC) wallet (we recommend Token Pocket Wallet) and send BNB to your BSC wallet address.

⇒ Now you can easily swap your BNB for $Rabbitking with Slippage 6%. Please remember to leave a small amount of BNB for transaction fees.
Congratulations, you are now part of the RabbitKing Family!

Token Address: 0x626cab57051e80f4b84551856588b62983bdb94e
